    prompt: 'Create and implement a comprehensive portfolio monitoring system that tracks performance metrics across all your cryptocurrency holdings',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Establishing systematic portfolio monitoring enables data-driven decision making and helps you identify when adjustments are needed to optimize performance or manage risk. Set up tracking for key metrics like total portfolio value, individual asset performance, allocation percentages, and profit/loss ratios using tools like spreadsheets or portfolio apps that sync with your exchanges. Regular monitoring helps you spot trends, evaluate the effectiveness of your investment strategy, and maintain awareness of your overall crypto allocation relative to your total investment portfolio.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-49',
    prompt: 'Execute your first cryptocurrency profit-taking strategy by selling 25% of your best-performing position to lock in gains',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Taking profits from successful investments is a crucial skill that prevents you from giving back all gains during market downturns and helps you realize actual returns rather than just paper profits. Choose your best-performing cryptocurrency that has gained 50%+ and sell a quarter of your position, then use those profits to either rebalance into underperforming assets or build your cash reserves. This disciplined profit-taking teaches you to overcome the psychological difficulty of selling winners while ensuring you capture real gains from your successful investment decisions.'
  }
];</parameter>
